Funded.club uses AI-assisted tools as part of our candidate sourcing and screening process. All applications are reviewed by a human recruiter, who makes all decisions about which candidates to progress.&nbsp;If your application seems like a good fit for the position, a real member of our team will contact you soon!Find Jobs in Germany on Arbeitnow

